OL,3,CBlue Plaque unveiled on island's
OL,4,Coldest-running residential home
OL,6,FA Blue Plaque has been unveiled to
OL,7,Fcommemorate the woman who founded
OL,8,FGuernsey's oldest-running residential
OL,9,Fhome.
OL,11,FMary Magdalene Edith Louisa Renouf,
OL,12,Fknown as Edith, was commemorated for
OL,13,Ffounding Le Platon Home outside the
OL,14,Fhome on Friday 8 November.
OL,16,FGuernsey's former Bailiff, Richard
OL,17,FCollas, unveiled Edith's plaque,
OL,18,Fdescribing her as a "modest, generous
OL,19,Fphilanthropist".
