OL,6,FFollowing the unveiling, Richard
OL,7,Fexplained: "Her legacy will continue.
OL,8,FIt will remind people of her because I
OL,9,Fsuspect that there aren't many people
OL,10,Fliving today who know her (despite
OL,11,Fbeing) well known in her lifetime.
OL,13,F"Unlike any other Blue Plaque on this
OL,14,Fisland, it is on a building that is
OL,15,Fstill very much associated with her
OL,16,Fwhich makes this plaque very special
OL,17,Fand absolutely unique."
