OL,4,Coldest-running residential home
OL,6,FNuns from the order of The Sisters
OL,7,FHospitaller of the Sacred Heart of
OL,8,FJesus have continued to move to
OL,9,FGuernsey over the past century.
OL,11,FIn 1927, Edith donated all her
OL,12,Fpersonal wealth to Le Platon, which
OL,13,Fremains the oldest residential home in
OL,14,FGuernsey.
OL,16,FBefore her death, Edith was conferred
OL,17,Fan MBE by King George VI in 1952.
